import React from 'react'

export const PieChartLegend = (data) => {
  const { style, x, y } = data
    console.log(data.data[0].number)
  const sum = data.data[0].number + data.data[1].number
  console.log(sum, x ,y)
  return (
    <svg>
      <g>
        <circle cx={x} cy={y} r="7" fill={style.fill} />
      </g>
      <text x={x+200} y={y}>
        {data.data[0].number}
      </text>
      <text x={x + 200} y={y+30}>
        {data.data[1].number}
      </text>
      <text x={x+200} y={y + 30} fontSize={25}>
        {data.data[0].number / sum * 100}%
      </text>
    </svg >
  )
}
